# Anxiety Disorders

This section contains educational notes and practical summaries about anxiety disorders, with a focus on clinically useful concepts for learners and healthcare professionals.

## Purpose
- Provide a structured overview of anxiety disorders
- Support clinical reasoning and differential diagnosis
- Offer concise, educational content in Portuguese

## Planned subtopics
- Core symptoms and clinical presentation
- Differential diagnosis
- Functional impact and comorbidities
- Practical treatment overview
- Patient education points

> Note: Content in this repository is for educational purposes only and does not replace formal clinical training or individualized medical care.
